{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c6bda37e1f","title":"政治上的持久战","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"32bca60ff4","index":0,"year":1938,"month":12,"day":15,"articleId":"c6bda37e1f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f92f1551f8","type":"paragraph","text":"政治上的持久战！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"c6bda37e1f"},{"id":"736ce81939","type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年12月15日）抗日的持久战需要的时间很长，要经过很多变化，我们打日本必须要有一个政治上的持久战。所以，每个革命者在政治上要有持久性，要准备应付各种曲折，准备克服困难。世界上无论什么事情都是走曲线，而不是走直线。这个向题也就是走“之”字路还是走“一”字路。无论什么事情都是走“之”字路，而不是走“一”字路，走“之”字路是世界上任何事情发展的原则。我们抗日战争要经过防御、相待和反攻三个阶段，这也是走“之”字路[1]这是毛泽东对抗大即将分配工作的八大队（女生大队）学员作关于","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"c6bda37e1f"}],"page":{"id":"c186a22699","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"c6bda37e1f","start":87,"end":87}}}},"__N_SSG":true}